text: Bangalaia maublanci is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Villiers in 1938, originally under the genus Sternotomiella. It is known from Gabon. It contains the varietas Bangalaia maublanci var. postvittata.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia maublanci. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1938
